{"vv53:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv53:0.2":"Purisavimana ","vv53:0.3":"Maharathavagga ","vv53:0.4":"3. Chattamanavakavimanavatthu ","vv53:1.1":"“Yo vadatam pavaro manujesu, ","vv53:1.2":"Sakyamuni bhagava katakicco; ","vv53:1.3":"Paragato balaviriyasamangi, ","vv53:1.4":"Tam sugatam saranatthamupehi. ","vv53:2.1":"Ragaviragamanejamasokam, ","vv53:2.2":"Dhammamasankhatamappatikulam; ","vv53:2.3":"Madhuramimam pagunam suvibhattam, ","vv53:2.4":"Dhammamimam saranatthamupehi. ","vv53:3.1":"Yattha ca dinna mahapphalamahu, ","vv53:3.2":"Catusu sucisu purisayugesu; ","vv53:3.3":"Attha ca puggaladhammadasa te, ","vv53:3.4":"Sanghamimam saranatthamupehi. ","vv53:4.1":"Na tatha tapati nabhe suriyo, ","vv53:4.2":"Cando ca na bhasati na phusso; ","vv53:4.3":"Yatha atulamidam mahappabhasam, ","vv53:4.4":"Ko nu tvam tidiva mahim upaga. ","vv53:5.1":"Chindati ramsi pabhankarassa, ","vv53:5.2":"Sadhikavisatiyojanani abha; ","vv53:5.3":"Rattimapi yatha divam karoti, ","vv53:5.4":"Parisuddham vimalam subham vimanam. ","vv53:6.1":"Bahupadumavicitrapundarikam, ","vv53:6.2":"Vokinnam kusumehi nekacittam; ","vv53:6.3":"Arajavirajahemajalachannam, ","vv53:6.4":"Akase tapati yathapi suriyo. ","vv53:7.1":"Rattambarapitavasasahi, ","vv53:7.2":"Agarupiyangucandanussadahi; ","vv53:7.3":"Kancanatanusannibhattacahi, ","vv53:7.4":"Paripuram gaganamva tarakahi. ","vv53:8.1":"Naranariyo bahuketthanekavanna, ","vv53:8.2":"Kusumavibhusitabharanettha sumana; ","vv53:8.3":"Anilapamuncita pavanti surabhim, ","vv53:8.4":"Tapaniyavitata suvannachanna. ","vv53:9.1":"Kissa samyamassa ayam vipako, ","vv53:9.2":"Kenasi kammaphalenidhupapanno; ","vv53:9.3":"Yatha ca te adhigatamidam vimanam, ","vv53:9.4":"Tadanupadam avacasi ingha puttho”ti. ","vv53:10.1":"“Sayamidha pathe samecca manavena, ","vv53:10.2":"Satthanusasi anukampamano; ","vv53:10.3":"Tava ratanavarassa dhammam sutva, ","vv53:10.4":"Karissamiti ca bravittha chatto. ","vv53:11.1":"Jinavarapavaram upehi saranam, ","vv53:11.2":"Dhammancapi tatheva bhikkhusangham; ","vv53:11.3":"Noti pathamam avocaham bhante, ","vv53:11.4":"Paccha te vacanam tathevakasim. ","vv53:12.1":"Ma ca panavadham vividham carassu asucim, ","vv53:12.2":"Na hi panesu asannatam avannayimsu sappanna; ","vv53:12.3":"Noti pathamam avocaham bhante, ","vv53:12.4":"Paccha te vacanam tathevakasim. ","vv53:13.1":"Ma ca parajanassa rakkhitampi, ","vv53:13.2":"Adatabbamamannitho adinnam; ","vv53:13.3":"Noti pathamam avocaham bhante, ","vv53:13.4":"Paccha te vacanam tathevakasim. ","vv53:14.1":"Ma ca parajanassa rakkhitayo, ","vv53:14.2":"Parabhariya agama anariyametam; ","vv53:14.3":"Noti pathamam avocaham bhante, ","vv53:14.4":"Paccha te vacanam tathevakasim. ","vv53:15.1":"Ma ca vitatham annatha abhani, ","vv53:15.2":"Na hi musavadam avannayimsu sappanna; ","vv53:15.3":"Noti pathamam avocaham bhante, ","vv53:15.4":"Paccha te vacanam tathevakasim. ","vv53:16.1":"Yena ca purisassa apeti sanna, ","vv53:16.2":"Tam majjam parivajjayassu sabbam; ","vv53:16.3":"Noti pathamam avocaham bhante, ","vv53:16.4":"Paccha te vacanam tathevakasim. ","vv53:17.1":"Svaham idha panca sikkha karitva, ","vv53:17.2":"Patipajjitva tathagatassa dhamme; ","vv53:17.3":"Dvepathamagamasim coramajjhe, ","vv53:17.4":"Te mam tattha vadhimsu bhogahetu. ","vv53:18.1":"Ettakamidam anussarami kusalam, ","vv53:18.2":"Tato param na me vijjati annam; ","vv53:18.3":"Tena sucaritena kammunaham, ","vv53:18.4":"Uppanno tidivesu kamakami. ","vv53:19.1":"Passa khanamuhuttasannamassa, ","vv53:19.2":"Anudhammappatipattiya vipakam; ","vv53:19.3":"Jalamiva yasasa samekkhamana, ","vv53:19.4":"Bahuka mam pihayanti hinakamma. ","vv53:20.1":"Passa katipayaya desanaya, ","vv53:20.2":"Sugatincamhi gato sukhanca patto; ","vv53:20.3":"Ye ca te satatam sunanti dhammam, ","vv53:20.4":"Manne te amatam phusanti khemam. ","vv53:21.1":"Appampi katam mahavipakam, ","vv53:21.2":"Vipulam hoti tathagatassa dhamme; ","vv53:21.3":"Passa katapunnataya chatto, ","vv53:21.4":"Obhaseti pathavim yathapi suriyo. ","vv53:22.1":"Kimidam kusalam kimacarema, ","vv53:22.2":"Icceke hi samecca mantayanti; ","vv53:22.3":"Te mayam punareva laddha manusattam, ","vv53:22.4":"Patipanna viharemu silavanto. ","vv53:23.1":"Bahukaro anukampako ca sattha, ","vv53:23.2":"Iti me sati agama diva divassa; ","vv53:23.3":"Svaham upagatomhi saccanamam, ","vv53:23.4":"Anukampassu punapi sunemu dhammam. ","vv53:24.1":"Ye cidha pajahanti kamaragam, ","vv53:24.2":"Bhavaraganusayanca pahaya moham; ","vv53:24.3":"Na ca te punamupenti gabbhaseyyam, ","vv53:24.4":"Parinibbanagata hi sitibhuta”ti. ","vv53:25.1":"Chattamanavakavimanam tatiyam. "}